          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Voluntary Protection Program Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides statutory authority for the Occupational Safety and Health Administration's (OSHA's) voluntary protection program, under which management, labor, and OSHA establish cooperative relationships at workplaces that have implemented a comprehensive safety and health management system.</p>]]></text>
